QuestData.Title: Future-Fresh Fungi
QuestData.Description:
A delicious mushroom? Alternate futures are not pantries to be raided for midmorning snacks.
But still... I would be lying if I said I had never dreamed of eating Rumi and Morsel's cooking again.
Very well! You have my permission to pass through the portal, though I advise you to find others to travel with.
My wardens have mentioned these dark mushrooms to me before. Apparently, they never stay in the same place for very long. Make of that what you will.
QuestData.LogDescription: Capture 7 Time-Blasted Trufflettes from the Primalist Future.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Return to Rumiastrasza at The Ruby Feast in Valdrakken.

Objectives.Objective: Use the portal to Primalist Tomorrow
